629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=fbb0fea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"2df2245bc101a4287a31dc9d82be8fa6cbfc7053","tid":1777881,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"598f62a5ccd514530f0cceef65af57e100ac405e","tid":1777881,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"揾吓啲揾工tg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"入過d 都係冇新工介紹"},{"pid":"3c14fc0ae65843e5796907682d037a610d0f4da1","tid":1777881,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"一星期內出糧個d 我都ok"},{"pid":"380e072d213d2a7004c8a25af4e0f80197697a0c","tid":1777881,"uid":333543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"入啲wts grp"},{"pid":"40a7362c7b196c8122e80214383ddfbb727def92","tid":1777881,"uid":333543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"例如:<br />\n<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/LlfsJYwznGT7YfjdmVNSs0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchat.whatsapp.com%2FLlfsJYwznGT7YfjdmVNSs0&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=6486d34b\" data-auto-link target=\"_